Package: dPCRfit
Type: Package
Title: Fit regression models to digital PCR data
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Adrian",
           family = "Lison",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "adrian.lison@bsse.ethz.ch",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6822-8437"))
Maintainer: Adrian Lison <adrian.lison@bsse.ethz.ch>
Description: Fit regression models to gene concentrations measurements obtained 
    via digital PCR (dPCR). A replacement for `lm` that uses a dPCR-specific 
    likelihood function, accounting for concentration-dependent measurement 
    error and non-detects.
